      • QuantileLayerPlot

        public QuantileLayerPlot(Plot p,
                         int a,
                         double[] q,
                         double r,
                         boolean _symetric)
        Build a quantile plot based on given plot. The quantile is drawn as a linear gradient from the base plot dots.
        Parameters:
        p - base plot
        a - axis number of quantile : 0=X quantile, 1=Y quantile, 2=Z quantile
        q - array of quantiles values
        r - rate of the quantile. The gradient line length is q/r
        _symetric - if yes, quantiles are drawn on both negative and positive sides of base plot dots
